---
title: Easy Pesto Pork & Veggie Mash with Tomato Salad
description: We've teamed juicy pork loin with a garlic and herb seasoning for a recipe you can't go wrong with. Complete with a hearty
veggie mash and a crisp salad on the side. This is a fun and nutritious take on your everyday pork steak!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-pork-veggie-mash-b3f4537d.jpg
